### Variables
@base = https://connectionpointchurch.breezechms.com/api
@key = {{$dotenv CHECKIN_BREEZE_API_KEY}}

### List attendance for an event instance
POST {{base}}/events/attendance/list?instance_id={{instance_id}}
Api-Key: {{key}}

### Delete attendance — all people from an event instance
# Set instance_id below, then run "List attendance" above to get person_ids
# @name listForDelete
POST {{base}}/events/attendance/list?instance_id={{instance_id}}
Api-Key: {{key}}

### Delete attendance — single person from event instance
POST {{base}}/events/attendance/delete?instance_id={{instance_id}}&person_id={{person_id}}
Api-Key: {{key}}

### Add attendance
POST {{base}}/events/attendance/add?instance_id={{instance_id}}&person_id={{person_id}}
Api-Key: {{key}}

### List events (today)
GET {{base}}/events?start={{$datetime iso8601 0 d}}
Api-Key: {{key}}

### List events (custom date range)
GET {{base}}/events?start={{start_date}}&end={{end_date}}
Api-Key: {{key}}

### Get eligible people for check-in
POST {{base}}/events/attendance/eligible?instance_id={{instance_id}}
Api-Key: {{key}}

### Get person details
GET {{base}}/people?details=1&filter_json={"id":"{{person_id}}"}
Api-Key: {{key}}
